					<div>
						<label class="sd2-label" for="sd2-v2-garage-year">Year</label>
						<select class="sd2-field" id="sd2-v2-garage-year" data-v2-garage-field="year" disabled>
							<option value="">Select Engine First</option>
						</select>
					</div>
					<div class="sd2-v2-garage-form__actions">
						<button class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--primary sd2-btn--full" type="submit">Save Vehicle</button>
						<a class="sd2-v2-garage-shop" href="&mvte:urls:SRCH:auto;" data-v2-garage-shop hidden>
							<span>View Parts for My Truck</span>
							<small data-v2-garage-shop-label></small>
						</a>
					</div>
				</form>

				<div class="sd2-v2-garage-saved" data-v2-garage-saved-wrap hidden>
					<h3 class="sd2-v2-garage-saved__title">Saved Vehicles</h3>
					<div data-v2-garage-saved-list></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</aside>
	</div>

	<div class="sd2-v2-cart-drawer" data-v2-cart>
		<div class="sd2-v2-cart-scrim" data-v2-cart-close></div>
		<aside class="sd2-v2-cart-panel" aria-hidden="true" role="dialog" aria-label="Cart">
			<div class="sd2-v2-cart-panel__head">
				<strong>Your Cart (<span data-hook="mini-basket-count"><mvt:if expr="l.settings:global_minibasket:basket_count GT 0">&mvte:global_minibasket:basket_count;<mvt:else>0</mvt:if></span>)</strong>
				<button class="sd2-v2-cart-panel__close" type="button" data-v2-cart-close aria-label="Close cart">
					<svg class="sd2-icon sd2-icon--lg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 6l12 12M18 6 6 18"/></svg>
				</button>
			</div>

			<div class="sd2-v2-cart-vehicle is-empty" data-v2-cart-vehicle>
				<svg class="sd2-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 12l1.5-5A2 2 0 0 1 6.4 5.5h11.2A2 2 0 0 1 19.5 7L21 12"/><path d="M3 12h18v5a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-1a1 1 0 0 1-1-1v-1H6v1a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1v-5Z"/></svg>
				<span data-v2-cart-vehicle-text>Add your truck to confirm fitment</span>
				<a href="&mvte:urls:SFNT:auto;" data-v2-garage-toggle>Add</a>
			</div>

			<div class="sd2-v2-cart-panel__body">
				<mvt:if expr="l.settings:global_minibasket:basket_count GT 0">
					<div class="sd2-v2-cart-lines" data-v2-cart-items>
						<mvt:foreach iterator="item" array="global_minibasket:groups">
							<mvt:do file="g.Module_Library_DB" name="l.success" value="Product_Load_Code(l.settings:item:code, l.settings:item_product)" />
							<mvt:do file="g.Module_Feature_URI_UT" name="l.settings:item:uri" value="Store_Product_URL(l.settings:item_product, NULL)" />

							<article class="sd2-v2-cart-item">
								<a class="sd2-v2-cart-item__media" href="&mvt:item:uri;"><img src="&mvte:item:imagetypes:main;" alt="&mvte:item:name;" loading="lazy"></a>
								<div class="sd2-v2-cart-item__body">
									<h3><a href="&mvt:item:uri;">&mvt:item:name;</a></h3>
									<p class="sd2-v2-cart-item__meta">SKU &mvte:item:code; <span> / Qty &mvte:item:quantity;</span></p>
									<mvt:foreach iterator="option" array="item:options">
										<p class="sd2-v2-cart-item__option">&mvt:option:attr_prompt;: <mvt:if expr="l.settings:option:option_id">&mvt:option:opt_prompt;<mvt:elseif expr="NOT ISNULL l.settings:option:data">&mvt:option:data;<mvt:elseif expr="NOT ISNULL l.settings:option:data_long">&mvt:option:data_long;</mvt:if></p>
									</mvt:foreach>
									<a class="sd2-v2-link-button" href="&mvte:urls:_self:auto_sep;Basket_Line=&mvte:item:line_id;&amp;Action=RPRD">Remove</a>
								</div>
								<strong class="sd2-v2-cart-item__price">&mvt:item:formatted_subtotal;</strong>
							</article>
						</mvt:foreach>
					</div>
				<mvt:else>
					<div class="sd2-v2-cart-empty" data-v2-cart-empty>
						<span class="sd2-v2-cart-empty__mark" aria-hidden="true">0</span>
						<p class="sd2-v2-cart-empty__title">Your Build Starts Here.</p>
						<p class="sd2-v2-cart-empty__copy">Choose your truck, then add fitment-confirmed parts with confidence.</p>
						<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--primary sd2-btn--full" href="&mvte:urls:SFNT:auto;">Explore Parts</a>
					</div>
				</mvt:if>
			</div>

			<div class="sd2-v2-cart-panel__foot">
				<div class="sd2-v2-cart-panel__subtotal">
					<span>Subtotal</span>
					<span data-v2-cart-subtotal><mvt:if expr="l.settings:global_minibasket:basket_count GT 0">&mvt:global_minibasket:formatted_total;<mvt:else>&mdash;</mvt:if></span>
				</div>
				<a class="sd2-btn sd2-btn--primary sd2-btn--full" href="&mvte:urls:BASK:auto;">View Cart &amp; Checkout</a>
			</div>
		</aside>
	</div>
</div>

<main class="sd2-cp sd2-guide sd2-guide--duramax">
	<section class="sd2-cp__hero" aria-labelledby="sd2-dmax-title"><div class="sd2-cp__hero-media" aria-hidden="true"><img src="https://sinisterdiesel.com/mm5/graphics/00000001/8/Generated%20image%203.png" alt="" fetchpriority="high"></div><div class="sd2-cp__shell sd2-cp__hero-grid"><div><p class="sd2-cp__eyebrow">Install Lab / GM diesel</p><h1 id="sd2-dmax-title">Duramax<br>install guides.</h1><p class="sd2-cp__lede">Identify the engine code first. Then verify model year, product fitment and current instructions before starting the installation.</p><div class="sd2-cp__actions"><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--primary" href="#engines">Find your Duramax</a><a class="sd2-cp__button" href="install-tutorials-overview.html">All tutorials</a></div></div><aside class="sd2-cp__hero-console"><span class="sd2-cp__console-kicker">GM engine map</span><strong>Six codes.<br>One clear start.</strong><div class="sd2-cp__console-data"><span>LB7 / LLY / LBZ</span><span>LMM / LML</span><span>L5P / 2017â€“current</span></div></aside></div></section>
	<div class="sd2-cp__signal"><div><span>01</span><strong>Identify the engine code</strong></div><div><span>02</span><strong>Match product and model year</strong></div><div><span>03</span><strong>Review access and routing</strong></div></div>
	<section class="sd2-cp__section" id="engines" aria-labelledby="sd2-dmax-engines"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><div class="sd2-cp__section-head"><div><p class="sd2-cp__label">Engine-code index</p><h2 id="sd2-dmax-engines">Choose the Duramax under your hood.</h2></div><p>Small model-year breaks can change hardware, routing and fitment. Use the engine code and live product application together.</p></div><nav class="sd2-guide__jump" aria-label="Duramax engines"><a href="#lb7">LB7</a><a href="#lly">LLY</a><a href="#lbz">LBZ</a><a href="#lmm">LMM</a><a href="#lml">LML</a><a href="#l5p">L5P</a></nav><div class="sd2-guide__engine-grid">
		<article class="sd2-guide__engine" id="lb7"><span>01 / 2001â€“2004</span><h3>LB7</h3><p>Early Duramax routing and component guidance for airflow, cooling and fuel-system upgrades.</p><a href="srch.html?Search=LB7+Duramax">Shop LB7 parts <b>&rarr;</b></a></article>
		<article class="sd2-guide__engine" id="lly"><span>02 / 2004.5â€“2005</span><h3>LLY</h3><p>Confirm the mid-year engine change before matching intake, charge-air and support parts.</p><a href="srch.html?Search=LLY+Duramax">Shop LLY parts <b>&rarr;</b></a></article>
		<article class="sd2-guide__engine" id="lbz"><span>03 / 2006â€“2007</span><h3>LBZ</h3><p>Use LBZ-specific applications to plan cooling, intake, filtration and engine-bay work.</p><a href="srch.html?Search=LBZ+Duramax">Shop LBZ parts <b>&rarr;</b></a></article>
		<article class="sd2-guide__engine" id="lmm"><span>04 / 2007.5â€“2010</span><h3>LMM</h3><p>Verify the 2007 model-year split and existing modifications before installation.</p><a href="srch.html?Search=LMM+Duramax">Shop LMM parts <b>&rarr;</b></a></article>
		<article class="sd2-guide__engine" id="lml"><span>05 / 2011â€“2016</span><h3>LML</h3><p>Plan fitment for later GMT900 trucks using the exact product code and application notes.</p><a href="srch.html?Search=LML+Duramax">Shop LML parts <b>&rarr;</b></a></article>
		<article class="sd2-guide__engine" id="l5p"><span>06 / 2017â€“current</span><h3>L5P</h3><p>Review late-model packaging, connection points and current product instructions.</p><a href="srch.html?Search=L5P+Duramax">Shop L5P parts <b>&rarr;</b></a></article>
	</div></div></section>
	<section class="sd2-cp__section sd2-cp__section--dark" aria-labelledby="sd2-dmax-system"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><div class="sd2-cp__section-head"><div><p class="sd2-cp__label">Job planning</p><h2 id="sd2-dmax-system">Understand the system before changing it.</h2></div><p>The guide library connects engine identification with the part overview and product-specific documentation needed to prepare correctly.</p></div><div class="sd2-cp__feature-grid"><article><span>01 / Airflow</span><h3>Intake routing</h3><p>Confirm air-box, sensor and filter placement for your exact generation.</p></article><article><span>02 / Charge air</span><h3>Pipes and boots</h3><p>Review connection points and clearance before removing factory plumbing.</p></article><article><span>03 / Cooling</span><h3>Coolant path</h3><p>Work on a cool engine and follow product-specific fill and inspection steps.</p></article><article><span>04 / Support</span><h3>Ask before work</h3><p>Send the truck year, engine code and product code to Parts Tech Support.</p></article></div><div class="sd2-cp__actions"><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--primary" href="install-part-overviews.html">Open part overviews</a><a class="sd2-cp__button" href="install-instructions.html">Download instructions</a></div></div></section>
	<section class="sd2-cp__section sd2-cp__faq" aria-labelledby="sd2-dmax-faq"><div class="sd2-cp__shell sd2-cp__faq-grid"><div><p class="sd2-cp__label">Duramax checks</p><h2 id="sd2-dmax-faq">Avoid the wrong engine path.</h2></div><div class="sd2-cp__accordions"><details open><summary>Why does the engine code matter?</summary><p>Duramax generations can overlap calendar years and use different components. The engine code is more precise than selecting â€œ6.6L Duramaxâ€ alone.</p></details><details><summary>Can a guide cover every trim and previous modification?</summary><p>No. Inspect the truck and compare it with the current instructions. Aftermarket components may change access, routing or compatibility.</p></details><details><summary>Where do I get product-specific help?</summary><p>Contact Parts Tech Support with the vehicle year, engine code, product code and clear photos of the installation area.</p></details></div></div></section>
	<section class="sd2-cp__final"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><div><p class="sd2-cp__label">Verify the application</p><h2>Match the part to the engine before work.</h2></div><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--light" href="help-sinister-diesel-parts-tech-support.html">Parts Tech Support</a></div></section>
</main><mvt:comment>
	Footer Experience V2 â€” additive, inactive. Real Miva constructs reused
	verbatim from cssui-global-footer.mvt: navigationset('links_resources'/
	'help_center'/'links_help'), contentsection('store_hours'/'site_copyright'),
	social_* flags, &mvt:global:store:*; fields. Build Log cards below use
	placeholder content pending real content/blog Miva integration in a later
	milestone â€” not fabricated as final copy.
</mvt:comment>

